{
  "stem": "2002.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He tried to influence the army, all the [? volunteers. ?] And-- and that's the time [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that's-- then when I--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that time I knew, because when we-- before we reached Berlin, I was in Lublin in the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went in in the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I already knew what was going on in-- in-- we [? were in ?] a city--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, with-- with I was all the time with the army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was 1944.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, when I went in in the army, we started to move out from Moscow, yes?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We moved out from Moscow, and I was very lucky.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I got a very good job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I got 20 trucks under me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "First I dove a general in a Jeep.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was the chauffeur.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was driving-- and the reason I'm talking so fast, I'm letting out a lot of stuff.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We only got so much time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So because what happened is I was a chauffeur for a general.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the general liked me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He wanted the camp to take out people to send to Stalingrad, where it was terrible there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The general took me out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And somehow I didn't go to Stalingrad, and I was staying in that battalion.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I got about 20 trucks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What was my job?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My job was to move, transportation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If the army kitchen is here, and the bakery, the kitchen, you know, so if the Germans were chased, we had to move another 20 miles.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So me and the trucks would do that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were told to deliver ammunition to the front line.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We would do almost-- all kind of work.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
